snippet.title: Measuring temperature  - Celsius and Fahrenheit degrees
snippet.description: I compare Celsius and Fahrenheit scales for measuring temperature and give some ballpark temperatures for both. Lastly, I solve simple problems about rising or dropping temperatures using integers.
